        "Description": "Good evening, 47. I have an update. by digging into the evidence even further, we have identified The Terrorist´s leader´s brother. \rHis name is Abdul Chabra. By eliminating him we will cause our main target to act and possibly reveal his identity.  You will also need to take down his &quot;Cleaners&quot;. Those people are covering all of his and Terrorist leader´s tracks.\r I will leave you to prepare.",
